2/1477066-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477066-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=ded93256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477066-20190827.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a8e0b57e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477066-20190827.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"算係第一次正式講明「不接受」五大訴求？咁大家要繼續堅持！行動繼續升級！大大力鍊政府春袋！鍊到佢要叫救命！<br />\n<br />\n條例草案梗係唔係問題癥結！係導火線咋！問題癥結係「雙普選」啊！屌你老母！過撚左2個月都唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撇除政府問題，淨係計警隊，再淨係計721 85 811 新屋嶺 CCTV直送，已經夠哂理由比示威者做任何野，包括以武制暴 以眼還眼 百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，設立死線，立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"f65c81fbb2dae85199abfc32949a4f0f5bca2376","tid":1510101,"uid":188050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zaX5PNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzaX5PNc.jpg&h=2ce9ecf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個先係話事大家仲未知?"},{"pid":"92eafeca0a0a3dbee07828425b4be4cc22b4c2f6","tid":1510101,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"唔壞步對咩撚野話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263853b55380fa0ce5584a8866bf4e1f06d60310","tid":1510101,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f6cf74936c331250dc0012185746dcf59ece7c","tid":1510101,"uid":258230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"撤回啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"6b1f98aea529360fb5c3c99608b4459668808c16","tid":1510101,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"我地都唔接受你做特首"},{"pid":"b9cff20968aa8c06f97be7a9937922f7b8120de0","tid":1510101,"uid":181778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"149347d628575dc687828e256f05a6240083271b","tid":1510101,"uid":126115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b1f98aea529360fb5c3c99608b4459668808c16","tid":1510101,"uid":103325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"我地都唔接受你做特首"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T0